This is Perl module App::tinyls.

INSTALLATION

Install cpanm (App::cpanminus) and then run the following command to install
App::tinyls:

    $ cpanm App::tinyls

If you get an archive of this distribution, unpack it and build it
as per the usual:

    $ tar xzf App-tinyls-$version.tar.gz
    $ cd App-tinyls-$version
    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

App::tinyls documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc App::tinyls

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

